      <div class="card" id="intro">
        <h1>Leasyback API Documentation <span class="pill">v1.0</span></h1>
        <p class="muted">This document describes the HTTP API for Leasyback. Endpoints use JSON and return standard HTTP status codes. Provide JWT tokens in the <code>Authorization</code> header where required.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card" id="conventions">
        <h2>Conventions</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Content type: <code>application/json</code></li>
          <li>Timestamps use ISO 8601 (UTC).</li>
          <li>Errors return a JSON body with a descriptive message and an appropriate 4xx/5xx status.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card" id="auth">
        <h2>Authentication</h2>
        <p>Authenticated endpoints require a JWT:</p>
        <pre><code>Authorization: Bearer &lt;JWT_TOKEN&gt;</code></pre>
      </div>

      <!-- 1 Register -->
      <div class="card" id="register">
        <h2>1. Register</h2>
        <div class="endpoint"><span class="method POST">POST</span> <code>/auth/register</code></div>
        <h3>Request</h3>
        <pre><code class="json">{
  <span class="k">"user_email"</span>: <span class="s">"test@gmail.com"</span>,
  <span class="k">"password"</span>: <span class="s">"12345678"</span>,
  <span class="k">"user_type"</span>: <span class="s">"Privatkunde"</span>
}</code></pre>
        <p class="muted">Acceptable <code>user_type</code> values: <code>Privatkunde</code>, <code>Firmenkunde</code>, <code>Werksatatt</code>, <code>Admin</code></p>
        <h3>Response 200</h3>
        <pre><code class="json">{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {
    "created_at": "2025-11-11T15:11:52.643534Z",
    "user_email": "test@gmail.com",
    "user_id": "65a75cf6-d62b-4a93-ab60-3a427ccec33d",
    "user_type": "Privatkunde"
  },
  "message": "User registered"
}</code></pre>
      </div>

      <!-- 2 Login -->
      <div class="card" id="login">
        <h2>2. Login</h2>
        <div class="endpoint"><span class="method POST">POST</span> <code>/auth/login</code></div>
        <h3>Request</h3>
        <pre><code class="json">{
  "user_email": "test@gmail.com",
  "password": "12345678"
}</code></pre>
        <h3>Response 200</h3>
        <pre><code class="json">{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {
    "token": "JWT_TOKEN",
    "user_type": "Privatkunde",
    "user_id": "65a75cf6-d62b-4a93-ab60-3a427ccec33d"
  },
  "message": "Login successful"
}</code></pre>
      </div>

      <!-- 3 Change Password -->
      <div class="card" id="change-password">
        <h2>3. Change password</h2>
        <div class="endpoint"><span class="method POST">POST</span> <code>/auth/changepassword</code></div>
        <div class="auth">Requires: Authorization header</div>
        <pre><code>Authorization: Bearer &lt;JWT_TOKEN&gt;</code></pre>
        <h3>Request</h3>
        <pre><code class="json">{
  "current_password": "12345678",
  "new_password": "1234567800"
}</code></pre>
        <h3>Response 200</h3>
        <pre><code class="json">{
  "message": "Password updated successfully"
}</code></pre>
      </div>

      <!-- 4 B2B Create -->
      <div class="card" id="b2b-create">
